 “重金属发源地”伯明翰的 The Crown 获得列入名单https://www.nme.com/news/music/birthplace-of-heavy-metal-birminghams-the-crown-secures-listed-status-3602827?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=birthplace-of-heavy-metal-伯明翰皇冠确保上市地位Liberty DunworthMon, 18 Mar 2024 16:05:58 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3602827 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="黑色安息日：老头子巴特勒、托尼·伊奥米、比尔·沃德和奥兹·奥斯本" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>黑色安息日 (Black Sabbath)、瘦丽兹 (Thin Lizzy)、犹大牧师 (Judas Priest) 等人都曾在此演出</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/birthplace-of-heavy-metal-birminghams-the-crown-secures-listed-status-3602827">“重金属发源地”伯明翰的 The Crown 获得上市地位的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="黑色安息日：老头子巴特勒、托尼·伊奥米、比尔·沃德和奥兹·奥斯本" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Black-Sabbath@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑色安息日</a>乐队首次演出的伯明翰历史悠久的酒吧已获得列入名单的地位，因为人们担心它可能会被拆除。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-to-lose-10-per-cent-of-grassroots-venues-in-2023-as-calls-grow-for-rest-of-industry-to-invest-3499727">随着要求其他行业投资的呼声越来越高，英国将在 2023 年失去 10% 的基层场馆</a></strong></li></ul><p>皇冠音乐厅也被一些人视为“重金属的发源地”，它是车站街上面临风险的建筑之一。它与英国最古老的电影院 Electric 位于同一条街上，该电影院已于上周关闭。</p><p>现在，根据历史英格兰的建议，它已被文化、媒体和体育部列为二级，以确保其在街道上的未来。</p><p>这个标志性的空间已经空置了 10 年，伯明翰开放媒体最初计划购买并修复这家酒吧。话虽如此，鉴于伯明翰议会的资金危机，该组织失去了资金，并面临着来自想要使用该地块建造住房的开发商的竞争。</p><p>超过 15,000 人签署了一份请愿书，呼吁拯救这条街道，并将其视为“公民自豪感、文化价值和历史资产的场所”（来自<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2024/mar/15/the-crown-pub-birmingham-grade-ii-listed-black-sabbath-heavy-metal" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a> ），随后该街道被列入名单。新的地位为场馆提供了更多保护，使其免受重新开发的影响。</p><p>该场地自 1881 年起就位于街上，曾举办过一些摇滚界大腕的表演。 Black Sabbath 不仅在该网站上演出了许多首场演出，而且还见证了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thin-lizzy">Thin Lizzy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-who">The Who</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/supertramp">Supertramp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duran-duran">Duran Duran</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/status-quo">Status Quo</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/judas-priest">Judas Priest</a>等乐队在其职业生涯早期成为头条新闻。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4p2HxWLbFt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width